                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-1525" type="given" value="JOSEPH GLISSON"></interp>JOSEPH GLISSON BUCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am foreman to Mrs. Lloyd. On Sunday morn<lb></lb>ing I saw the cart at Dowsett's—it is Mrs. Lloyd's cart, I am quite sure.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
