                  </hi>. On the 10th of Dec. last I saw Mellson—he repre<lb></lb>sented</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184404080232"></xptr>
               <p>himself <hi rend="italic">to</hi> be a wine-merchant, not a woollen-merchant—Purdy re<lb></lb>presented himself as the servant, and took me <hi rend="italic">to</hi> Mellson as a wine-merchant.</p>
